id:
CF_NAME create-isolation-segment SEGMENT_NAME

NOTES:
   The isolation segment name must match the placement tag applied to the Diego cell.

CF_NAME install-plugin (LOCAL-PATH/TO/PLUGIN | URL | -r REPO_NAME PLUGIN_NAME) [-f]

EXAMPLES:
   CF_NAME install-plugin ~/Downloads/plugin-foobar
   CF_NAME install-plugin https://example.com/plugin-foobar_linux_amd64
   CF_NAME install-plugin -r My-Repo plugin-echo

CF_NAME terminate-task APP_NAME TASK_ID

EXAMPLES:
   CF_NAME terminate-task my-app 3
